data.oai_dc:dc: This spreadsheet contains synonymies between the species used in PHYLACINE Version 1.2.0, previous versions of this database, and other popular databases like EltonTraits and IUCN. It also contains information on the phylogenetic placement of species in PHYLACINE. Unlike Synonymy_table_valid_species_only, this spreadsheet also contains species that were not accepted in PHYLACINE Version 1.2.0 but are accepted in other databases like EltonTraits and IUCN.
